{"body": "Science Fiction:\n\n```ruby\nmodule ActiveSupport\n  class Deprecation\n    def initialize(horizon = default_horizon, gem_name = 'rails')\n      self.deprecation_horizon = horizon\n      self.gem_name = gem_name\n    end\n\n    def default_horizon\n      \"#{ActiveSupport::VERSION::MAJOR}.#{ActiveSupport::VERSION::MINOR + 1}\"\n    end\n  end\nend\n```\n\nbecause sometimes it should be `major + 1`. Or maybe it should be always `major +1` and never `minor + 1` ?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5812979", "created_at": "2012-05-20T22:31:03Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6348#issuecomment-5812979", "updated_at": "2012-05-20T22:31:03Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6348, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/paneq", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/9b81cae1fb43808ac23a2188258ca9e4?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F180bb054f1a36e1777b05a0664a7eb71.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/received_events", "gravatar_id": "9b81cae1fb43808ac23a2188258ca9e4", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "paneq", "type": "User", "id": 65587, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paneq/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e6380bd354364b900f9c9"}, "id": 5812979, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6348"}
